Description: Velocity limitation via input.A velocity limitation can be activated via a digitalinput.In operating mode Profile Torque, the minimumvelocity is internally limited to 100 RPM.Modified settings become active immediately.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 3006:1EhModbus 1596Profibus 1596CIP 106.1.30ModbusTCP 1596EtherCAT 3006:1EhPROFINET 1596
